[src:electrolytic-capacitor/aeg-german-company] The dimensions of the building were chosen to allow turbines to be transported above other machinery.
[src:electrolytic-capacitor/aeg-german-company] In the 1920s, AEG became a global supplier of electrical know-how and equipment.
[src:electrolytic-capacitor/aeg-german-company] In 1923, for example, it provided most of the essential materials and a team of engineers to oversee the electrification of British-ruled Palestine.
